sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as 🌐 Client (SDK)
    participant EC as 📥 Event Collector
    participant K as 📨 Kafka
    participant DS as ⚡ Decision Service
    participant S as 🔍 Signals (6x)
    participant RE as 📏 Rule Engine
    participant CS as 📋 Case Service
    participant WH as 🔔 Webhook

    C->>+EC: POST /v1/events<br/>(API Key: sk_test_...)
    EC->>EC: Validate schema<br/>(AJV per-type)

    alt Invalid Event
        EC-->>C: 400 Bad Request
        EC->>K: DLQ (5s timeout)
    end

    EC->>K: Publish to<br/>signalrisk.events.raw
    EC-->>-C: 202 Accepted

    K->>+DS: Consumer poll

    par Signal Aggregation (Promise.allSettled, 150ms timeout)
        DS->>S: device-intel
        DS->>S: velocity (Redis)
        DS->>S: behavioral
        DS->>S: network-intel
        DS->>S: telco-intel
        DS->>S: graph-intel (Neo4j)
    end

    S-->>DS: Signal responses<br/>(or timeout/circuit open)

    DS->>DS: Renormalize weights<br/>for available signals

    DS->>+RE: Evaluate DSL rules
    RE-->>-DS: Rule outcomes<br/>+ weighted score

    DS->>DS: Final score →<br/>ALLOW / REVIEW / BLOCK

    DS->>K: Publish to<br/>signalrisk.decisions

    DS->>DS: Cache in Redis<br/>(5s TTL)

    DS-->>-C: Decision ready

    par Downstream Processing
        K->>CS: REVIEW/BLOCK →<br/>Create case
        K->>WH: Sign & deliver<br/>webhook (HMAC-SHA256)
    end

    Note over CS: Analyst reviews<br/>in Dashboard

    CS->>K: Feedback →<br/>signalrisk.feedback
    K->>RE: Adjust rule weight<br/>(+0.05 fraud / −0.03 FP)
